data.description:
Inviting 3-bed, 2-bath brick home with an attached 2-car garage awaits you! This delightful one-level residence boasts a concrete patio and a spacious driveway with a convenient walkway extending to the rear patio, perfect for hosting outdoor gatherings.

Inside, discover a kitchen designed for convenience, featuring an abundance of cabinetry and a pantry with pull-out shelving, making organization a breeze. The laundry room is a practical delight with a wash sink, a folding table, and ample cabinet space for all your storage needs.

What sets this home apart is the custom fireplace mantle, fueled by gas logs, providing warmth to the interior as well as the attached garage. Don't miss this meticulously maintained gem - schedule your viewing today!
